    },
    "^[%@ conversation](inflect: true) · ^[%@ file](inflect: true) · %@": {
      "comment": "A line of text that provides information about a project, including the number of conversations, files, and the last time the project was updated. The first argument is the number of conversations. The second argument is the number of files. The third argument is the formatted relative time since the project was last updated.",
